description: Etws: Table containing Ericsson-specific Early Warning System (ETWS) data with details on event time, location, cell IDs, and various identifiers.  Columns: dateTime (Event timestamp), Area_Name (Geographic area), CellId (Cell identifier), Id2 (Secondary cell identifier), Id3 (Another cell or equipment identifier), Id4 (Auxiliary identifier, likely constant here), vsDataType (Data type identifier, constant here), vsDataFormatVersion (Version of the data format, constant here), Etws.etwsId (ETWS message identifier).
